body.content:
📥 **New Intake Item Captured**

**Sender:** @{coalesce(first(body('HTTP_GetIntakeSummary')?['items'])?['sender'], triggerOutputs()?['body/from'])}
**Subject:** @{coalesce(first(body('HTTP_GetIntakeSummary')?['items'])?['subject'], triggerOutputs()?['body/subject'])}
**Summary:** @{coalesce(first(body('HTTP_GetIntakeSummary')?['items'])?['summary'], triggerOutputs()?['body/bodyPreview'])}

**Outcome:** @{body('HTTP_PostIntakeMessage')?['processing_complete']?['outcome']}
**Filed to:** @{coalesce(body('HTTP_PostIntakeMessage')?['processing_complete']?['target_folder'], 'left in Inbox (needs review)')}

🔗 **LCC Item:** @{coalesce(first(body('HTTP_GetIntakeSummary')?['items'])?['lcc_item_url'], concat(parameters('LCC_HOST'), '/#/inbox'))}
📧 **Open Email (Desktop):** @{coalesce(first(body('HTTP_GetIntakeSummary')?['items'])?['email_url_desktop'], concat('ms-outlook://open?url=', encodeUriComponent(coalesce(body('HTTP_GetEmailWebLink')?['web_link'], triggerOutputs()?['body/webLink'], ''))))}
🌐 **Open Email (Web):** @{coalesce(first(body('HTTP_GetIntakeSummary')?['items'])?['email_url'], body('HTTP_GetEmailWebLink')?['web_link'], triggerOutputs()?['body/webLink'])}

_Run:_ @{body('HTTP_PostIntakeMessage')?['correlation_id']}
